<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>The<sp/>work<sp/>on<sp/>the<sp/>project<sp/>is<sp/>structured<sp/>as<sp/>follows:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>There<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>pool<sp/>of<sp/>tasks,<sp/>they<sp/>are<sp/>gradually<sp/>replenished.<sp/>You<sp/>can<sp/>find<sp/>those<sp/>in<sp/>our<sp/>main<sp/>project<sp/>on<sp/>Github.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">2.<sp/>During<sp/>meetings,<sp/>these<sp/>tasks<sp/>are<sp/>distributed<sp/>among<sp/>the<sp/>performers.<sp/>You<sp/>can<sp/>also<sp/>pick<sp/>one<sp/>that<sp/>you<sp/>see<sp/>fit,<sp/>just<sp/>don&apos;t<sp/>forget<sp/>to<sp/>assign<sp/>it<sp/>yo<sp/>yourself.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">3.<sp/>While<sp/>performing<sp/>the<sp/>task,<sp/>you<sp/>need<sp/>to<sp/>create<sp/>a<sp/>draft<sp/>pull<sp/>request,<sp/>where<sp/>you<sp/>need<sp/>to<sp/>put<sp/>your<sp/>works,<sp/>so<sp/>that<sp/>team<sp/>can<sp/>check<sp/>in<sp/>which<sp/>direction<sp/>the<sp/>development<sp/>is<sp/>moving.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">4.<sp/>When<sp/>the<sp/>developer<sp/>decides<sp/>that<sp/>the<sp/>work<sp/>is<sp/>finished,<sp/>he<sp/>withdraws<sp/>the<sp/>pull<sp/>request<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>draft<sp/>state.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">5.<sp/>The<sp/>code<sp/>is<sp/>checked<sp/>by<sp/>the<sp/>whole<sp/>team,<sp/>and<sp/>if<sp/>there<sp/>are<sp/>any<sp/>errors,<sp/>they<sp/>are<sp/>corrected.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">6.<sp/>After<sp/>permission<sp/>is<sp/>given<sp/>the<sp/>code<sp/>is<sp/>merged<sp/>into<sp/>the<sp/>dev<sp/>branch.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">7.<sp/>Performer<sp/>asks<sp/>for<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>task.</highlight></codeline>
